I don't know how I can feel empty,depressed,tired,stressed,joyful,and happy all in 1 minute of every hour of every day.I feel empty ...I don't know why.Maybe it's because I let someone go...and I hardly talk to that anonymous person.and I really miss that person...cuz we had a lot of good times...and it DEPRESSES me because...like I don't see that person anymore...and I'm hoping that person can be in my quincenera and..I feel depressed cuz it's just hard to like...I  dunno...i guess my icon...really describes how I feel. "You can never let go your FIRST L<3ve" And...if you guessed Richard...than yes you're right.I'm tired and pressured by my damn soccer coach.I can't be in two EFFIN places at once!I almost broke me effin' ankle this past saturday. I was center midfield...and i'm usually center forward..and so i had just helped the defense cuz our DEFENSE DOESNT MOVE!so then i get the ball and pass it up...and allie should have been there cuz i was yellin' her name to be open...and he's like "WHERE THE HECK IS MY CENTER MIDFIELD!?" and i'm like "OVER HERE!" and i passed the ball and the other team got it and i got it back and dribbled it up ...and its just stressful cuz i'm in one place and he yells at me and tells me i have to be in another.he's effin new at coaching soccer and it pissed me off how he doesn't know how to line us up!...and i'm goalie and i'm suprised...i'm doing really good!omg JeRoMe might go to my game this saturday!...anyways and i'm stressed cuz of school...my homework is piling and i have yearbook...and i have...an english teacher that pretty ....getting like whoa.i dunno but thank GoD i don't talk during that class.and...mr.rabalais ...i miss him!i want religion to be taught by the one and only mr.r...but other than that the whole thing messin' up my life is richard...and...i dunno it hurts to know that we're not as close as we were and how we don't talk...but who blames me?!i mean...the boy is sometimes online i'm RARELY online nowadays because of soccer then spring select is coming up and i have a possibility of making that.=/ and...just alot...of crap.but i mainly feel empty..and depressed.i come home everyday sad because of my mixed feelings then...someone in my class hating me for no reason.=/ makes it worse..and i just need one person who understands how i feel..i need someone who can just come up to me and say i'm dreaming...cuz every day it gets worse.somehow.until someone talks to me...i think i'll be ok..but i just need to talk to someone.my feelings are just..i dunno i guess u can say they are hard to understand unless u've really have had that experience.

Sorry I haven't updated in a long.I've been really busy lately.With school and soccer and stuff.=/ "And I wrote this letter in my head cuz so many things were left unsaid. But now you're gone and I can't think straight!" "Somehow I can't put you in the past.I'd do AnYtHiNg" "Will you remember me?Cuz I know I won't forget you." Saturday:Had a soccer game!oh my effin Gosh!I was goalie for two quarters and the defense on my team...like depend on the goalie.i always land up one on one if Hayley doesn't reach the area on time.=/ Thank God for Hayley and Nicole!=) We lost though.I'm gonna ask my mom if I can watch JeNn JeN's game this coming Saturday.Natalie slept over we stayed up and talked a lot.Drank a LOT OF COFFEE!we were like WHOA!lol neighbors spoke to my cousin and me.=/
Sunday:Had fun with Stephanie and Natalie.Neighbors were like...staring =/lol.went to church and stayed for the youth group meeting.Kevin...and I were like whoa.it was just funny.u just had TO SEE US!lmao.and...spoke to JeRoMe @ night 4 TWO HOURS!But WE had a good convo.!=)it was a long good convo. then stayed up a bit

OK...Wednesday was the LA County Fair.OMG SO MUCH FUN!i LOVED IT.like 20 minutes after lunch we combined groups with anthony. so my group was jeselle claudia jessica andrea and denise. and we combined with martin alex e. tommy josh jake and anthony. and today we went to the cathedral!saw lots of boys. and like the quizzes^ i was ...like bored...omg the imagine by john lennon is so like freaky cuz my yarn art is that and i have a pic of the tribute to john lennon from nyc.and i just came back from...jamie's house. she gave me a tour of her house...and like we played volleyball and played in her tree house.haha.and we played pool and like just chilled haha.how fun.lol well i'm doing quizzes so byes.=/ i'm bored.=)

Ok...so my team tied with Long Beach (soccer) 2-2 umm i played forward first quarter,second quarter i was goalie...i was suprised on how well i did at the worse position in soccer history, and 3rd quarter i was center forward again...4th quarter  i didnt get to play...and here's why:
In 3rd quarter i had the mall i was running and...like this girl came up to me and like...tried to get the ball one of her legs was between mine and like she kicked and made my right leg go to the right and i jumped and she pushed and i landed on the floor on my right knee really hard. (and earlier during the summer i hit that knee cuz ...of my cousin and so its sensitive) and like all that pain when i first hit it earlier in the summer came back like it was like whoa!and so i stayed on the floor crying cuz it hurt like HELL!and coach had to pick me up off the field.cuz i couldnt walk at the moment.and like...i was replaced and i couldnt play and now i cant like go to practice unless i have gone to the doctor and like have a note saying i'll be able to play.i can walk now but i dunno about running.so yeah. i have to go to doctor and it still kind of hurts....BOscO tEcH lost against BOscO 8-0.umm so yeah.=/my soccer game was really rough.allie couldnt breathe in second quarter so she had to take that quarter off and what not.so yeah.wow.i have to hop in the shower..no i gotta get ready for a party.and i got two hugs from thomas today.aww i miss him.he's gonna call me tomorrow.=)i saw nathan,antonio,joey,angel and dylan...and i didn't know moe and kevin were on football <they were playing today.so wow.yeah.got a hug from nathan and dylan...gtg.

<FONT color=#3366ff>i know i didn't know  him or talk to him...but... i had a dream... (and no this isn't gonna be a dream like martin luther king jr.) i had a dream about chris castillo.i know what u're thinking you didn't even talk to him..but i've seen him but thats not the point...well i had a dream about him and jessica and i were at his funeral jessica was already crying and the casket hasn't passed us yet.and when it did (i was closest to the aisle) when i saw him i began to cry.just looking at him and the marks made me cry.and so later throughout the dream i was comforting and holding jessica and we walked up to the casket and i cried more.just looking at him made me cry.and jessica and i were hugging and crying and my mom came to take me home but i refused and stayed with jessica.and she let me.and we just kept crying. and when i woke up i was crying because of the sight i saw in my dream.i don't like seeing ppl who died.then when i woke up and i was already crying flashbacks came to my mind when i saw my uncle in his casket and saw the marks from the car accident then my nephew who didn't reach his 4th day after birth and watching his mom cry over the casket before the burial.it was sad.and 'til this point i still am.not crying but sad.</FONT>

well...my week was ok.
Monday:did nothing but go out to eat with jackie and chad and my parents.
Tuesday:umm...for p.e. we had to dance... so i chose alex to be my partner (alex e.) and we were cha chaing.lol fun VERY FUN!
Wednesday:umm hung out with jake and enrique.fun...we're gonna go over jake's house on the 24.
Thursday: hung out with jake and enrique.had soccer practice...lol FUN..shit...i got my uniform i'm stinkin @$$ number 2!!!who the hell gets 2?!well..uh...and our uniform is the shit!my uniform is hott. my uniform is black and yellow with a stripe on each sleeve!and it's like bosco tech colors...and mrs.o'connor suggested i should go to thomas' football games in my uniform.thomas will be going to my soccer games!how fun!lol
Friday:Did nothing but talk to Anthony all day!What made my day today cuz i was sad...but what made my day was when i saw the name Ringo Starr in my English book.lmao i know i'm easily entertained and alex started tickling me because i tickled him and he said "it's not obvious" (<it's our thing) and ....he also tickled me because he said i was too quiet today.and anthony and jake kept making me laugh.and my little brother is JORDAN!we're both short brown hair and dimples!yup my little brother is awesome!i <3 him! he laughs so cute...he laughs like woody woodpecker but cuter!lol i <3 him!and i want to see thomas and especially denise!i haven't seen Denise in ages.ok ok i saw her saturday but that was because of my sisters engagement party.woo!and...today i might go to bosco's football game if it's home.i'm gonna ask john if he can go (if it's home!) woo.hmmm...allie and i yesterday at practice...were like WOO ppl thought we were crazy coach would tell us to demonstrate a hard yet easy drill and we're like "What?" in a high voice lol we had fun yesterday and we were hyper.and like she was goalie then i was...and lmao...when i blocked the goals i yelled before i started i was like "i'm going to do reenaactments of allie!" and everyone was laughing.coach isn't that strict on how we act.its just the way we do the drill is what he's strict about but when he wants us to be serious...he'll tell us. and if we do something we have to run around the whole park.=/ sucky yes i know thank God allie and i know when to stop.=) lol haha well...hmm....hayley goes to josephs.haha allie goes to mayfair.and yeah.so us three have fun but yesterday it was just allie and me cuz hayley was tired.

<FONT color=#009900>Ok My sister's engagement party yesterday was fun!umm before it got really completely dark...like before 9 my cousins and i were going down a small hill on this giant skateboard.pretty fun!and getting piggy back rides...and getting piggy back rides while the person giving u the ride is on the skooter!<that was super fuN!when natalie left...denise had just gotten there...and so denise and i were talking in the room my cousins and i always hang out in.and then we played blackjack and poker with my nephew david (we placed bets with cookies=) earlier we did the same but without denise cuz she wasn't there) lol and....we listened to music.so yeah yesterday was fun.before denise came my nephew david and i have our usual talks..but..like..this time it got like really serious...that i cried.so yeah</FONT>

Well school went ok.It wasn't all great...but it was ok. Well my parents,my brother, and me all sat down and talked about me going to high school.Well these are the schools my parents and my brother decided to have me apply to:
1)St. Josephs (Of course!My brother,mom,and dad all suggested Josephs)
2)Mater Dei (My brother suggested...as well as my dad...since my brother said he'd be more than happy to take me to Mater Dei and pick me up after school too.And since my dad works near Mater Dei I can walk to the bus stop for OCTA and take the bus close to where my dad works.{Since my daddy works for OCTA I can get a free bus pass}But my brother is willing to take me and pick me up.)
3)Our Lady of the Rosary (In Fullerton.My brother suggested this school because it's also a good school and he's willing to take me and pick me up.Hmmm So Until my parents change their minds...those are the schools I'm applying to.) =)
